---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Real Estate Agent Mount Gravatt Brisbane | Daniel Gierach"
  description="Daniel Gierach, real estate agent in Mount Gravatt Brisbane. Well-connected suburb with strong lifestyle amenity and buyer demand. Ray White Bulimba. Call 0412 523 821."
>

<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Real Estate Agent Mount Gravatt Brisbane",
  "description": "Daniel Gierach is a specialist real estate agent in Mount Gravatt Brisbane, serving the southern suburbs.",
  "url": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/mount-gravatt",
  "breadcrumb": {
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Mount Gravatt", "item": "https://www.danielgierach.com/suburbs/mount-gravatt" }
    ]
  }
})}</script>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 1: HERO
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#1c1917; color:#f2efe9; padding: 100px 24px 80px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Mount Gravatt</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:1.5rem; color:#f2efe9;">
      Real Estate Agent<br/><em style="color:#f5d07a;">Mount Gravatt.</em>
    </h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4bc; max-width:580px; margin:0 auto 2.5rem;">
      Specialist property sales in Mount Gravatt and Brisbane's southern suburbs.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/listings" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">View Current Listings</a>
      <a href="/appraisal" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">Request an Appraisal</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: WHY THIS AREA
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Well-connected living with strong buyer demand.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Mount Gravatt offers a strong combination of accessibility, lifestyle amenity and value. Its central location, good schools and the Westfield Garden City precinct make it consistently attractive to a wide range of buyers.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I understand the buyer profile active in Mount Gravatt and the surrounding southern suburbs. Whether family home or investment, I build campaigns that attract the right buyers and generate genuine competition.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Griffith University's Mount Gravatt campus brings a steady flow of student and academic residents that underpins rental yields in the suburb and sustains investor demand across multiple market cycles. Westfield Garden City on Kessels Road is one of Brisbane's premier shopping destinations and its presence within the suburb adds day-to-day convenience that family buyers consistently rate highly. The Pacific Motorway interchange gives Mount Gravatt fast access to both the CBD and the Gold Coast, broadening the buyer pool to include commuters from both directions. Recent sales data shows the suburb's detached house market has been particularly active among upgrading families seeking more space within a practical distance of the city.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Mount Gravatt Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Southern Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Well-Connected Suburb</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Broad buyer appeal</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/upper-mount-gravatt" style="color:#c4912a;">Upper Mount Gravatt</a>, <a href="/suburbs/mount-gravatt-east" style="color:#c4912a;">Mount Gravatt East</a>, <a href="/suburbs/tarragindi" style="color:#c4912a;">Tarragindi</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 3: SUBURBS SERVED
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#fff; padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:900px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Areas Covered</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Suburbs I specialise in.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr); gap:1.25rem;">
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Mount Gravatt</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Well-connected suburb with strong lifestyle amenity</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Mount Gravatt East</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Growing suburb with strong family appeal</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Upper Mount Gravatt</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Elevated living with views and good value</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Holland Park</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Established family suburb with leafy streets</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Tarragindi</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Quiet established suburb with family appeal</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Greenslopes</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Established suburb with consistent owner-occupier demand</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 4: HOW I CAN HELP YOU SELL
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Selling in Mount Gravatt</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:3rem;">What selling with Daniel looks like.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2.5rem; margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <div style="display:flex; gap:2rem; align-items:flex-start;">
        <span style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:300; color:#c4912a; line-height:1; flex-shrink:0; width:2.5rem;">1</span>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.2rem; font-style:italic; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Free appraisal</p>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#6b6560;">I'll walk you through what your property is worth and what buyers are currently paying in your area.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:2rem; align-items:flex-start;">
        <span style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:300; color:#c4912a; line-height:1; flex-shrink:0; width:2.5rem;">2</span>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.2rem; font-style:italic; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Tailored campaign</p>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#6b6560;">Every property is different. I build a strategy around your home, your timeline and your buyer profile.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:2rem; align-items:flex-start;">
        <span style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:300; color:#c4912a; line-height:1; flex-shrink:0; width:2.5rem;">3</span>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.2rem; font-style:italic; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Managed negotiation</p>
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#6b6560;">I manage every offer with commercial discipline to protect your final result.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/appraisal" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">Request a Free Appraisal</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 5: CTA STRIP
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#1c1917; color:#f2efe9; padding:80px 24px; text-align:center;">
  <div style="max-width:700px; margin:0 auto;">
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#f2efe9; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Thinking of selling in Mount Gravatt?</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.75; color:#c9c4bc; margin-bottom:2rem;">Call me directly for a no-obligation conversation about your property and what it could achieve in today's market.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      <a href="tel:+61412523821" style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2rem; font-weight:300; color:#f5d07a; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:0.02em;">0412 523 821</a>
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:transparent; color:#f2efe9; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block; border:1px solid #c4912a;">Send a Message</a>
      <a href="/appraisal" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">Request an Appraisal</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section div[style*="grid-template-columns:repeat(3"] {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr) !important;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    section div[style*="grid-template-columns:repeat(3"] {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>

</Layout>
